_xResult.title: Starlight, Starshine Dress
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made midi dress with Chantilly lace
_xResult.longdesc:
Take time to appreciate yourself in this custom made couture creation. This made to measure dress, perfect for evenings or formal events, is decadently crafted with delicate Chantilly lace, precious baby doll cuts and an effortlessly layered skirt.


The bodice is unlined lace, so be as daring as you desire. Or, use the button below to request a lining if you prefer to be more modest. You need a dress made custom to your measurements. You'll love the feeling of knowing it's made just for you and fits you perfectly!
